snippet.title: Epic Battle Fantasy 5 Trailer v2
snippet.description:
Epic Battle Fantasy 5 version 2 is a huge update that's currently in beta stage on Steam!
Buy it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/432350/Epic_Battle_Fantasy_5/

Trailer voiced by Andrew "Noves" Miller, music by Phyrnna, as always.

You can follow EBF5 news and play demos on my blog: http://kupogames.com
You can chat about the game on Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/5gnkTvE
You can throw some money at me and get perks on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/mattroszak
---
